Patch Set 1:

@Brian: As suggested in Skype I'm going to implement the changes necessary to 'fix' the kernel-ib-devel RPM in the lbuild script to automate the process. It'll be part of the second patch.
Purpose of this patch is to verify changes don't break the 'normal' compilation and to check that the SR-IOV enable Lustre can be build in Jenkins job 'lustre-reviews-vib'.
